cc:Work.dc:title: vCardTools Class Diagram a/o milestone 0.9
cc:Work.dc:description: A diagram of classes and relationships in the vCardTools PHP package (https://github.com/evought/VCard-Tools) a/o Milestone 0.9 (first usable release). Describes the current relationships between vCard, vCardDB, Template, and utlity classes. Specifically, it will be used to highlight some odd relationships which will be targets for future refactoring.
